		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#searchInput">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Social-democratic third party in Vermont</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the Vermont Progressive Party. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Progressive_Party_(disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect mw-disambig" title="Progressive Party (disambiguation)">Progressive Party (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
